import React from "react";
import PropTypes from "prop-types";
import { Form, FormLabel, Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap";

const PersonalInfo = ({
  firstName,
  lastName,
  password,
  confirmPassword,
  email,
  terms,
  updates,
}) => {
  return (
    <>
      <Row>
        <Col>
          <FormLabel>First Name</FormLabel>
          <Form.Control
            type="text"
            name="first-name"
            placeholder="Please fill your first name"
            value={firstName}
          />
        </Col>
        <Col>
          <FormLabel>Last Name</FormLabel>
          <Form.Control
            type="text"
            name="last-name"
            placeholder="Please fill your last name"
            value={lastName}
          />
        </Col>
      </Row>
      <FormLabel>Email Address</FormLabel>
      <Form.Control
        type="email"
        name="email"
        placeholder="Please fill your Email"
        value={email}
      />
      <FormLabel>Password</FormLabel>
      <Form.Control
        type="password"
        name="password"
        placeholder="Please choose password"
        value={password}
      />
      <FormLabel>Confirm Password</FormLabel>
      <Form.Control
        type="password"
        name="confirm-password"
        placeholder="Please enter your password again"
        value={confirmPassword}
      />
      <Form.Group>
        <Form.Check
          type="checkbox"
          name="terms"
          label="I Agree to terms & services"
          value={terms}
        />
        <Form.Check
          type="checkbox"
          name="updates"
          label="I Agree to recieve Emails containing updates and news about my account"
          value={updates}
        />
      </Form.Group>
    </>
  );
};

PersonalInfo.propTypes = {
  firstName: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
  lastName: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
  password: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
  confirmPassword: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
  email: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
  terms: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
  updates: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
};
export default PersonalInfo;
